      "id": "w_95612bf2db9c58_19dafc5c99d",
      "title": "Melodies Of The Abyss 2026",
      "artist": "Sam Iwata aka Liu",
      "year": "2025",
      "description": "Melodies of the Abyss unfolds as a brooding supernatural psycho-thriller, daring to imagine an intimate confrontation between Kurt Cobain and Courtney Love—or is it Lucifer Morningstar?\nInspired by the final, chaotic week of Kurt’s life, the narrative threads together two figures gripped by existential despair—one mortal, one divine.\nKurt seeks escape from the weight of a desperate pact that shattered more than just himself. What he truly needs is the courage to face its lingering shadows and reclaim what may still be redeemed. Lucifer, cast down in defiance, longs to rage against the heavens—but beneath the fury lies a yearning for the love of the God who cast him out.\nWith fractured memory as its canvas and spiritual unrest as its undercurrent, the film explores suffering not merely as consequence, but as communion—between abandonment and yearning, rebellion and redemption.",
